## Tech Stack

- **Frontend**: Next.js 15 (App Router), React 19, TypeScript, Tailwind CSS v4
- **Backend**: Next.js API Routes + tRPC, Zod validation
- **Database**: Supabase (Postgres, Auth, Row Level Security, Storage)
- **Edge**: Vercel Edge Middleware for redirects
- **Payments**: Stripe
- **Testing**: Vitest, Testing Library, Playwright

## Key Features (MVP)

- Authentication & multi-tenant organizations
- QR creation with downloadable SVG/PNG
- Link management with version history
- Public redirect service with analytics
- Dashboard with scan analytics
- Stripe billing (Free: 3 QRs, Pro: 100 QRs)

